  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tired of bland, terrible-looking linear games without much gameplay, full of stereotypes and plot holes? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Good news: this game isn't bland. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Step into the hilarious world of <i>Isekaing</i> -  truly triple-N(iche) game that combines parody, musical and quest genres into an unholy abomination that will challenge your very sanity! </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/b58e9eff52b6c21cce068d7503426f0f.poster.avif?t=1771601048\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/b58e9eff52b6c21cce068d7503426f0f.webm?t=1771601048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/b58e9eff52b6c21cce068d7503426f0f.mp4?t=1771601048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Zoe Powell is hit by the Truck-kun, and respawns into a retro video game, where she must face dangers in form of cliché, meaningless choices, a plot that has more holes than Swiss cheese, and other plagues of modern gaming. Also, every notable person is trying to sing her a song! Will she endure this torment? Probably yes, because she is the protagonist, but you can still buy this game and find out! You might be surprised. Or not. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>(CAUTION! Press \"read more\" button, or you will make one lonely goblin sad!)</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/ea4c261e2bf213463913dcf4ed07c320.poster.avif?t=1771601048\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/ea4c261e2bf213463913dcf4ed07c320.webm?t=1771601048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/ea4c261e2bf213463913dcf4ed07c320.mp4?t=1771601048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Here, you will be able to: </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Listen to shitton of dialogue that attempts to be funny </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Solve stupidly easy puzzles </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Fight even easier enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Face the vicious satire about all your favorite (and hated) things</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Enjoy (or suffer) the occasional singing<br>- Try to figure out all the game, movie, or other pop-culture references </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Be offended by everything (but that is not necessary)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/b71b3a44703bea96c6ce0a8fdd4fbfef.poster.avif?t=1771601048\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/b71b3a44703bea96c6ce0a8fdd4fbfef.webm?t=1771601048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/b71b3a44703bea96c6ce0a8fdd4fbfef.mp4?t=1771601048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Remakening is upon us!  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This free update opens a new chapter of the Isekaing story, while adding a real-time combat system, new songs, puzzles, and a lot more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the Unhollywood, the land where dreams became real, but now a dark shadow looms over the once peaceful kingdom. And it's full of shit! Visit classic fairytales twisted by the constant cash-grab remakes of the MOUSE corporation and its undead ruler, and do your worst to fix them, or... just survive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/272b57d0b9586f832e55be800490bb1e.poster.avif?t=1771601048\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/272b57d0b9586f832e55be800490bb1e.webm?t=1771601048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/272b57d0b9586f832e55be800490bb1e.mp4?t=1771601048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>So what are you waiting for? Yet another Isekai world awaits a new hero to save it!  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/aae418dad0366d330eba888c39df8b5f.poster.avif?t=1771601048\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/aae418dad0366d330eba888c39df8b5f.webm?t=1771601048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/aae418dad0366d330eba888c39df8b5f.mp4?t=1771601048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Seriously, why are you still reading this? Buy! The! Game!  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't you have wallets or something? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/ab94abc65f5ec7e55d2cc4f2ef4dad5c.poster.avif?t=1771601048\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/ab94abc65f5ec7e55d2cc4f2ef4dad5c.webm?t=1771601048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/ab94abc65f5ec7e55d2cc4f2ef4dad5c.mp4?t=1771601048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
