ome to the Unhollywood, the land where dreams became real, but now a dark shadow looms over the once peaceful kingdom. And it's full of shit! Visit classic fairytales twisted by the constant cash-grab remakes of the MOUSE corporation and its undead ruler, and do your worst to fix them, or... just survive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/272b57d0b9586f832e55be800490bb1e.poster.avif?t=1771601048\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/272b57d0b9586f832e55be800490bb1e.webm?t=1771601048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/272b57d0b9586f832e55be800490bb1e.mp4?t=1771601048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>So what are you waiting for? Yet another Isekai world awaits a new hero to save it!  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/aae418dad0366d330eba888c39df8b5f.poster.avif?t=1771601048\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/aae418dad0366d330eba888c39df8b5f.webm?t=1771601048\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055370/extras/aae418dad0366d330eba888c39df8b5f.mp4?t=1771601048\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Seriously, why are you still reading this? Buy! The! Game!  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Don't you have wallets or something? </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video cl